title: Lucky Bet 1943 Western - A Rodeo of Rhythm, Action and Romance! Starring Roy Rogers

sources.title: Lucky Bet 1943 Western - A Rodeo of Rhythm, Action and Romance! Starring Roy Rogers
sources.description:
A singing rodeo star (Roy Rogers) loses half of a ranch and enters a chuck-wagon race to win it back.


Original title: Song of Texas (1943)
Directed by Joseph Kane

Main cast:
Roy Rogers - Roy
Sheila Ryan - Sue Bennett
Barton MacLane - Jim Calvert
Arline Judge - Hildegarde

Genres: Western, Music
Release date: June 14, 1943
Filming location: Lone Pine, California


Black & Whit version: https://youtu.be/YAEdSdV5_rg
